arStrings.szText: "Lilith doesn't seem to believe that you destroyed Astaroth."
Of course not. Demons are arrogant creatures. She would never accept that our kind could vanquish Astaroth.
Brushing off the Player's statement, trying to sound confident.
What troubles me is why she is looking for him. What does she want?
Astaroth was from the Realm of Hatred, the place Lilith once called home. Perhaps therein lies an answer. I'll have to ponder this more.
